ORDER BY + LIMIT
1. ORDER BY (Sorting Data)
👉 ORDER BY = Arrange data (like sorting in Excel)
🔹 Basic Syntax
SELECT column_name
FROM table_name
ORDER BY column_name;
---
🔹 Example Table: students
id	name	age
1	Rahul	22
2	Amit	19
3	Neha	21

🔹 Sort by Age (Ascending - Default)
SELECT * FROM students
ORDER BY age;
👉 Output:
id	name	age
2	Amit	19
3	Neha	21
1	Rahul	22

---
🔹 Sort Descending (Highest First)
SELECT * FROM students
ORDER BY age DESC;
👉 Output:
id	name	age
1	Rahul	22
3	Neha	21
2	Amit	19

---
🔹 Sort by Name (Alphabetical)
SELECT * FROM students
ORDER BY name ASC;

---
🔹 Sort by Multiple Columns
SELECT * FROM students
ORDER BY age ASC, name DESC;

👉 Meaning:
First sort by age
If same age → sort by name

---
🎯 Real-Life Use
Sort employees by salary
Sort products by price
Sort students by marks

---
⛔ Common Mistake
❌ Wrong:
ORDER age BY
✅ Correct:
ORDER BY age
---

2. LIMIT (Control Number of Rows)
👉 LIMIT = “Give me only few rows”
---
🔹 Basic Syntax
SELECT * FROM table_name
LIMIT number;
---
🔹 Example
SELECT * FROM students
LIMIT 2;
👉 Output (only first 2 rows):
id	name	age
1	Rahul	22
2	Amit	19

---
🔥 ORDER BY + LIMIT (Most Important 🔥🔥)
👉 Used together in real jobs
---
🔹 Top 2 Oldest Students
SELECT * FROM students
ORDER BY age DESC
LIMIT 2;
---
🔹 Youngest Student
SELECT * FROM students
ORDER BY age ASC
LIMIT 1;
---
🔹 Top 3 Highest Salaries (Real Example)
SELECT * FROM employees
ORDER BY salary DESC
LIMIT 3;
---
📄 OFFSET (Bonus)
👉 Skip rows
SELECT * FROM students
LIMIT 2 OFFSET 1;
👉 Meaning:
Skip 1 row
Show next 2 rows
---
🧠 Real Scenario
👉 You want:
Latest 5 users
Highest 10 salaries
Top 3 scorers

👉 Always use:
ORDER BY + LIMIT
---
🎯 Practice Questions
1. Get all students sorted by age
2. Get top 2 youngest students
3. Get oldest student
4. Get top 3 names in alphabetical order
5. Skip first 2 and show next 3
---
💡 Final Summary
ORDER BY → Sort data
LIMIT → Restrict number of rows
Together → 🔥 Very powerful
---
🚀 Pro Tip
Always use ORDER BY with LIMIT
❌ Wrong:
SELECT * FROM students LIMIT 5;
👉 Random result
✅ Correct:
SELECT * FROM students
ORDER BY id DESC
LIMIT 5;


